<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>163</hymn_number>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Na hehpih hi tin ka gela,
 Zie bang lawm ding ei tam?
 Lili banga pak ding ka sak lai ka gam,
 A thim zo tai tai khuo a val ta puoi.

[V2]
 Aw Galili tuipi chunga Na thu gen kha,
 Suihlung ah gensawn kitin Lalpa;
 Buoina tui kinawk lai ahin,
 Panpih ka ngai ui.

[V3]
 2. Na nuoisieh tai ti'n ka gela,
 Zie bang hin a bawl thei;
 Na Belam na huonga umhaw gitloh na'n,
 A hihzak zo, nungtieng sulhei zo tau.

[V4]
 3. Gosen gama maute bang khan,
 Ka maunau hi ngaiin;
 Tuipi San gal na tutna chawnban hatin,
 Ei pui inla, nawp lenna ei tunin.

[V5]
 4. Thim lal theihna a kim phat leh,
 Hun etsak ding ka hi;
 Zinmang sala tang cheng le ka pawtsak thei,
 Keia haw chu lungin ngilh thei puong ie.</lyrics>
<title>Panpih Ka Ngai Ui</title>
</song>